# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — Android Project

## Project Overview
- **Package**: `{{PACKAGE_NAME}}`
- **Architecture**: Clean Architecture based on [NowInAndroid](https://github.com/android/nowinandroid)
- **Language**: Kotlin, Java 17
- **UI**: Jetpack Compose (Material 3)
- **DI**: Hilt
- **Async**: Coroutines + Flow
- **Navigation**: Navigation3 (Serializable NavKeys)
- **Database**: Room (KSP)
- **Network**: Retrofit2 + OkHttp
- **Image**: Coil

## Module Structure

| Module | Role |
|--------|------|
| `:app` | Entry point, navigation wiring |
| `:feature:*/api` | NavKey exports only |
| `:feature:*/impl` | ViewModel, Screen, feature logic |
| `:core:model` | Domain data classes |
| `:core:domain` | UseCases, Repository interfaces |
| `:core:data` | Repository impl, Hilt modules |
| `:core:database` | Room DAOs, Entities |
| `:core:network` | Retrofit services, DTOs |
| `:core:datastore` | Proto DataStore |
| `:core:designsystem` | Theme, Material 3 components |
| `:core:ui` | Shared screen-level composables |
| `:core:navigation` | Navigator, NavKey interface |

## Dependency Direction
```
:app → :feature:*/api, :feature:*/impl
:feature:*/impl → :core:ui, :core:domain, :core:data, :core:designsystem
:feature:*/api → :core:navigation
:core:data → :core:database, :core:network, :core:datastore, :core:model
:core:domain → :core:data, :core:model
```

## Key Patterns

- **ViewModel**: `@HiltViewModel` + `StateFlow` with `WhileSubscribed(5_000)`
- **Repository**: Offline-first (Room reads, background sync)
- **UseCase**: `operator fun invoke(): Flow<T>`, pure Kotlin
- **Navigation**: `@Serializable` NavKeys, Navigation3
- **DI**: `@Binds` for interfaces, `@Provides` for factories

